parameters.jsonBody:
=  {
    "trigger_id": "{{ $('Parse Webhook').item.json['response']['trigger_id'] }}",
    "external_id": "Idea Selector",
    "view": {
	"type": "modal",
	"callback_id": "certificate_request_modal",
	"title": {
		"type": "plain_text",
		"text": "Request New Certificate"
	},
	"submit": {
		"type": "plain_text",
		"text": "Request"
	},
	"close": {
		"type": "plain_text",
		"text": "Cancel"
	},
	"blocks": [
		{
			"type": "image",
			"image_url": "https://img.securityinfowatch.com/files/base/cygnus/siw/image/2022/10/Venafi_logo.63459e2b03b7b.png?auto=format%2Ccompress&w=640&width=640",
			"alt_text": "delicious tacos"
		},
		{
			"type": "input",
			"block_id": "domain_name_block",
			"label": {
				"type": "plain_text",
				"text": "Domain Name"
			},
			"element": {
				"type": "plain_text_input",
				"action_id": "domain_name_input",
				"placeholder": {
					"type": "plain_text",
					"text": "Enter the domain name"
				}
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "input",
			"block_id": "validity_period_block",
			"label": {
				"type": "plain_text",
				"text": "Validity Period"
			},
			"element": {
				"type": "static_select",
				"action_id": "validity_period_select",
				"placeholder": {
					"type": "plain_text",
					"text": "Select a validity period"
				},
				"options": [
					{
						"text": {
							"type": "plain_text",
							"text": "1 Year"
						},
						"value": "P1Y"
					},
					{
						"text": {
							"type": "plain_text",
							"text": "2 Years"
						},
						"value": "P2Y"
					}
				]
			}
		},
		{
			"type": "input",
			"block_id": "optional_note_block",
			"optional": true,
			"label": {
				"type": "plain_text",
				"text": "Optional Note"
			},
			"element": {
				"type": "plain_text_input",
				"action_id": "optional_note_input",
				"multiline": true,
				"placeholder": {
					"type": "plain_text",
					"text": "Add any extra information (e.g., usage context, urgency)"
				}
			}
		}
	]
}
}

values.content:
=Analyze the following VirusTotal scan results and summarize the overall risk as Low, Medium, or High based on the number of engines flagging the domain (excluding "clean" or "unrated" results). Use the following criteria for risk rating:

Low: No significant threats detected; domain is clean.
Medium: Minor issues detected; may require further review.
High: Significant threats like phishing or malware; manual review recommended.

Here are the scan results for the domain {{ $('Parse Webhook').item.json.response.view.state.values.domain_name_block.domain_name_input.value }}:

Malicious: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.malicious }}
Suspicious: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.suspicious }}
Undetected: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.undetected }}
Harmless: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.harmless }}
Timeout: {{ $json.data.attributes.last_analysis_stats.timeout }}
Reputation: {{ $json.data.attributes.reputation }}

Provide an overall risk rating and suggest next steps based on your analysis. Please keep it concise.

